The paper discusses the challenges of complex machine learning systems and the need for explainable AI to improve user trust and acceptance. This topic is highly relevant to the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category, as well as the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and the statistical learning theory (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the study involves a user study, which could be relevant to the cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-category.
